Release
LTS.400.4
of February 28, 2024
New features
New “Object chat” widget added: now chats can be assigned to system objects and access to chat depend on object permissions.
Autosave option added when moving objects between folders in registry.
deletePlainObjects functionality improved: now all objects in primitive type can be deleted.
nginx supported mTLS authentication option when receiving messages via ETL was added.
Processing of functions with EvaluateContextFunction is now performed when working with doAfterCommit function.
Added new Edoc feature: version comparison of two documents based on single template.
Changes and improvements
CI/CD operation was improved;
Filtering algorithms functionality was optimized;
Blocking algorithm functionality when working with integer attributes was improved;
Object visual display was improved;
Dashboard row display was stabilized;
Working with limit parameters was stabilized;
Selecting values of object attributes was stabilized;
Display of attribute percent values in registry was improved;
Converting contents of uploaded signature was stabilized;
Selection of created task’s object type when working with business process was improved;
Edoc functionality when downloading documents with comments and saving edited documents was improved;
Favorites filter was stabilized;
Display of Excel files downloaded from dashboards was stabilized;
Adding large amount of data from clipboard to Edoc was stabilized;
The parseSignature function for getting signature from external storage was updated.
